_dit（DiT分块计算）：\n大幅减少显着的占用占用，但会降低推理速度。\n\n## 🥒tile_size /tile_overlap（分块大小与重叠）：\n控制输入视频在推理时的分块方式。\n\n## 🥒unload_dit（卸载DiT模型）：\n解码前卸载DiT模型以降低速度显着存高，但会小幅降低。\n\n## 🥒local_range(上下文参考)\nlocal_range 值越大： 模型需要同时处理更多的视频帧数据。这意味着更高的计算成本、更大的显存占用和更长的处理时间。\nlocal_range 值越小： 模型处理的帧数较少，因此计算速度会更快，显存占用更低。\n"],"color":"#d8771c","bgcolor":"#a25915"},{"id":23,"type":"FlashVSRNode","pos":[-1483.9311908946063,646.8290728127824],"size":[283.194148127144,226],"flags":{},"order":4,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"frames","name":"frames","type":"IMAGE","link":27},{"localized_name":"model","name":"model","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"model"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"mode","name":"mode","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"mode"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"scale","name":"scale","type":"INT","widget":{"name":"scale"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"tiled_vae","name":"tiled_vae","type":"BOOLEAN","widget":{"name":"tiled_vae"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"tiled_dit","name":"tiled_dit","type":"BOOLEAN","widget":{"name":"tiled_dit"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"unload_dit","name":"unload_dit","type":"BOOLEAN","widget":{"name":"unload_dit"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"seed","name":"seed","type":"INT","widget":{"name":"seed"},"link":null}],"outputs":[{"localized_name":"image","name":"image","type":"IMAGE","links":[28,29]}],"properties":{"cnr_id":"flashvsr_ultra_fast","ver":"4820b3f02347bddcbbb9a5a85ab7638fe976366e","Node name for S&R":"FlashVSRNode","ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{"model":true,"mode":true,"scale":true,"tiled_vae":true,"tiled_dit":true,"unload_dit":true,"seed":true},"version":"7.5.2","input_ue_unconnectable":{}}},"widgets_values":["FlashVSR-v1.1","tiny-long",2,true,true,false,555729102760022,"randomize"]},{"id":20,"type":"ImageConcatMulti","pos":[-1178.1386675968113,985.9740762886553],"size":[272.431640625,150],"flags":{"collapsed":false},"order":6,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"label":"图像_1","localized_name":"image_1","name":"image_1","type":"IMAGE","link":24